article.description: — Taj Benning had a season-high 24 points, tying his career high, and Jake Wojcik added 20 points as Fairfield topped Rider 76-65 on Friday night.
article.headline: Benning carries Fairfield over Rider 76-65
article.story: LAWRENCEVILLE, N.J. -- — Taj Benning had a season-high 24 points, tying his career high, and Jake Wojcik added 20 points as Fairfield topped Rider 76-65 on Friday night. Benning hit 6 of 9 3-pointers. Wojcik also had eight rebounds. Supreme Cook had 11 points and seven rebounds for Fairfield (10-10, 4-5 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Allen Powell had 21 points for the Broncs (6-13, 2-7). Dimencio Vaughn added 17 points and nine rebounds. Dwight Murray, Jr. had six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
